places.name: Hotel Le Cercle - Tour Eiffel
places.description: Hôtel Le Cercle - Tour Eiffel ★★★ , completely renovated in 2020, offers you a warm welcome to the seventh arrondissement of Paris, one of the Capital's liveliest residential neighborhoods. The Eiffel Tower and the Champ de Mars are just steps away, and the École Militaire lies before you. Located in the prestigious avenue de la Bourdonnais, Le Cercle retains the intimacy and poetry of a Parisian home. In its chic and contemporary decor, our elegant hotel invites you to unwind in the refinement of typical Parisian houses. Located adjacent to the Eiffel Tower, the Champ de Mars, and the École Militaire, the Hôtel Le Cercle E boasts an ideal location from which to explore Paris. Countless must-see tourist attractions await, just minutes away on foot or by public transportation (from the École Militaire Métro/bus station): the Hôtel des Invalides, the Trocadéro Esplanade, the Alexandre III bridge, the Grand Palais, the Champs-Élysées shopping district and the Arc de Triomphe, the neighborhood of Saint-Germain-des-Prés, the Rodin Museum, the Quai Branly Museum, the Musée d'Orsay, the Garnier Opera House, the Montparnasse Tower, the Louvre… Right next to the Hotel Le Cercle, the Rue Cler offers you the opportunity to immerse yourself in the daily life of the neighborhood and its residents. This famous street is a favorite destination of true Parisian gourmets. On this lively, traditional, pedestrian street, you'll find exceptional food purveyors, many cafés and restaurants, wine merchants, delicatessens, master chocolatiers and pastry chefs, and more.

address_obj.address_string: 117 avenue de la Bourdonnais, 75007 Paris France
